OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCanada settles $2.8bn      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fresidential schools lawsuit
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Canada has agreed to pay C$2.8bn       
OL,6, ($2.9bn; #1.68bn) to settle a          
OL,7, class-action lawsuit seeking           
OL,8, compensation for the loss of language  
OL,9, and culture caused by its residential  
OL,10, school system.                         
OL,12,FGovernment-funded compulsory boarding  
OL,13,Fschools were part of a policy meant to 
OL,14,Fassimilate children and destroy        
OL,15,Findigenous cultures and languages.     
OL,17,FThe money will be paid to a non-profit 
OL,18,Ftrust independent of the government.   
OL,20,FBut the settlement must still be       
OL,21,Ffinalised and approved by a court.     
